<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[الاستحباب]</span>: استحبّه: أي أحبّه.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">واستحبّه عليه:</span> أي آثره.<span class="c5"> قال الله تعالى:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>فَاسْتَحَبُّوا الْعَمى عَلَى الْهُدى <span class="c2">«١»</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
